220
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:26,760
E va a...

221
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:32,720
Angelica Bove.

222
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:34,840
[APPLAUSI]
Con "Mattone".

223
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:40,480
