to listen to Adriano Celentano.

437
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:36,200
And many more. But Laura, of course.

438
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:39,200
- Grazie mille.
- Vogliamo iniziare?

439
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,200
